{%- comment -%}
  Renders the lab's QR codes & share cards as download cards.
  File paths come from _data/downloads.yml (editable in Sveltia CMS →
  "Downloads & QR codes"); the labels/blurbs describe fixed brand assets, so
  they live here. The HTML5 `download` attribute makes each button SAVE the
  file instead of just opening it.
{%- endcomment -%}
{% assign d = site.data.downloads %}

<p class="whl-dl-intro">
  Click <strong>Download</strong> to save a file. Every QR points to
  <strong>watershedhydrologylab.com</strong>. The boxes below are images — on a
  phone, long-press and choose “Download&nbsp;image”.
</p>

<h2 id="qr-codes">QR codes</h2>
<div class="whl-card-grid">
  <article class="whl-card">
    <div class="whl-dl-media"><img src="{{ d.qr_primary | relative_url }}" alt="Gradient QR code with the lab logo" loading="lazy"></div>
    <h3>Gradient + logo</h3>
    <p>The everyday QR — red→petrol gradient with the lab logo in the middle. Great for slides, flyers and email.</p>
    <div class="whl-btn-row">
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-primary" href="{{ d.qr_primary | relative_url }}" download><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download PNG</a>
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-ghost" href="{{ d.qr_primary | relative_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Preview</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="whl-card">
    <div class="whl-dl-media"><img src="{{ d.qr_dark | relative_url }}" alt="Solid dark QR code with the lab logo" loading="lazy"></div>
    <h3>Solid dark + logo</h3>
    <p>Single-colour dark QR with logo. Best on light paper or anywhere you need one ink colour.</p>
    <div class="whl-btn-row">
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-primary" href="{{ d.qr_dark | relative_url }}" download><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download PNG</a>
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-ghost" href="{{ d.qr_dark | relative_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Preview</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="whl-card">
    <div class="whl-dl-media"><img src="{{ d.qr_hires | relative_url }}" alt="High-resolution gradient QR code" loading="lazy"></div>
    <h3>High-resolution (300&nbsp;dpi)</h3>
    <p>Same gradient QR at print resolution. Use when printing larger than a business card.</p>
    <div class="whl-btn-row">
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-primary" href="{{ d.qr_hires | relative_url }}" download><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download PNG</a>
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-ghost" href="{{ d.qr_hires | relative_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Preview</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="whl-card">
    <div class="whl-dl-media whl-dl-doc"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
    <h3>Print PDF</h3>
    <p>Vector-quality PDF. Hand this to a print shop for posters or banners.</p>
    <div class="whl-btn-row">
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-primary" href="{{ d.qr_pdf | relative_url }}" download><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download PDF</a>
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-ghost" href="{{ d.qr_pdf | relative_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>

<h2 id="share-cards">Ready-to-share cards</h2>
<div class="whl-card-grid">
  <article class="whl-card">
    <div class="whl-dl-media"><img src="{{ d.card_landscape | relative_url }}" alt="Landscape share card with QR and lab name" loading="lazy"></div>
    <h3>Landscape card</h3>
    <p>Wide card with the QR + lab name. Drop into a slide or an email signature.</p>
    <div class="whl-btn-row">
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-primary" href="{{ d.card_landscape | relative_url }}" download><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download PNG</a>
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-ghost" href="{{ d.card_landscape | relative_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Preview</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="whl-card">
    <div class="whl-dl-media"><img src="{{ d.card_badge | relative_url }}" alt="Portrait badge card" loading="lazy"></div>
    <h3>Badge / name-tag</h3>
    <p>Portrait card sized for a conference badge or name-tag.</p>
    <div class="whl-btn-row">
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-primary" href="{{ d.card_badge | relative_url }}" download><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download PNG</a>
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-ghost" href="{{ d.card_badge | relative_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Preview</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="whl-card">
    <div class="whl-dl-media"><img src="{{ d.card_story | relative_url }}" alt="Instagram Story card" loading="lazy"></div>
    <h3>Instagram Story</h3>
    <p>1080×1920, ready to post as an Instagram or WhatsApp Story.</p>
    <div class="whl-btn-row">
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-primary" href="{{ d.card_story | relative_url }}" download><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download PNG</a>
      <a class="whl-btn whl-btn-ghost" href="{{ d.card_story | relative_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Preview</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
